    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently runs rough and will require significant mechanical attention, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows its age with several large dents, significant paint fading, and visible rust on the lower panels. The interior is heavily worn, with multiple tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is sold strictly as-is.",
