    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some minor dents and clear coat peeling on the hood, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at an affordable price point.",
